  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  title: Modify Pipeline by Script
  description: 'Whis this scene you can learn how to interact with Broccoli Pipelines
    using scripts; this way you can modify tree aspects using code, create variations
    at runtime or automatize the tree creation process.\n\nThe script containing
    the code to interact with the tree Pipeline is found in the ''Broccoli Tree Creator''
    GameObject on the Hierarchy Panel. The script is named ''Modify Pipeline''; you
    can interact with it on the Inspector Panel and inspect its code to learn how
    the processing gets done via scripting.


    Happy Tree Designing!'
  autoselectOnSceneLoad: 1
  develShowFields: 0
  scenePipelineType: 0
  detectedPipelineType: 0
  lastSaved: 0
